title: moving to a new city: making friends, feeling homesick & finding a new routine
itunes:title: moving to a new city: making friends, feeling homesick & finding a new routine
description:
Brooke and Danielle are BACK this week and debriefing on the weeks events in the city.  The gals attended a party with many NYC TikTokers, many of which were exactly as they appear online, but others were not.  The gals also dive into some advice for moving to a completely new city, practical tips for putting yourself out there, and how to navigate a lot of change.  Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening stories + screenshots on Instagram.
